---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ServiceExplore from '../../components/ServiceExplore.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="General Dentistry — Oasis Dental Care, Huntington Beach"
  description="Professional cleanings, exams, and preventive care for all ages in Huntington Beach. Led by Dr. Jason Fu at Oasis Dental Care. Call (714) 893-2106."
  page="services"
>

<section class="phero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumbs"><a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/services">Services</a><span class="sep">/</span><span style="color:#cfe6e2">General Dentistry</span></div>
    <span class="tag">General dentistry</span>
    <h1>General Dentistry</h1>
    <p>Your foundation for a healthy, confident smile—gentle care, every step of the way.</p>
    <div class="acts">
      <a class="btn" href="/contact">Book a consultation <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="tel:7148932106">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pad">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="split">
      <div>

        <div class="img-ph reveal">
          <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
          <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
          <span class="img-ph-desc">Clean, welcoming clinical setting or patient smiling in chair</span>
        </div>

        <div class="prose reveal">
          <span class="tag">Overview</span>
          <h2>Prevention, early detection, and lifelong support.</h2>
          <p>From routine checkups to professional cleanings and tooth-colored fillings, general dentistry is the foundation for healthy, lasting smiles. We focus on preventive care, early detection, and patient education.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose reveal" style="margin-top:48px">
          <h3>What Is General Dentistry?</h3>
          <p>General dentistry covers maintenance, prevention, and early detection across your whole mouth—teeth, gums, jaw, and overall well-being. Regular checkups and cleanings let us catch small issues before they become bigger problems.</p>

          <div class="img-ph reveal">
            <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
            <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
            <span class="img-ph-desc">Dentist examining patient in a friendly environment</span>
          </div>

          <h3>Who Is It For?</h3>
          <p>Everyone. Kids on their first visit, adults keeping their smiles strong, seniors preserving lifelong oral health. No judgment if it's been a while—just support at your pace.</p>

          <h3>What to Expect</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Health history review and open Q&amp;A</li>
            <li>Digital X-rays and full-mouth exam</li>
            <li>Professional cleaning (plaque + tartar removal)</li>
            <li>Personalized home care guidance</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="img-ph reveal">
            <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
            <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
            <span class="img-ph-desc">Digital X-ray in use, or hygienist performing cleaning</span>
          </div>

          <h3>Why Choose Oasis?</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Same doctor and staff, visit after visit</li>
            <li>Modern digital imaging for precise, clear results</li>
            <li>Unrushed appointments with clear explanations</li>
            <li>Welcoming for anxious patients and long-absent patients</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal" style="margin-top:48px">
          <span class="tag">Common questions</span>
          <h2 class="prose" style="margin-top:8px">Good to know.</h2>
          <div class="faq">
            <details open><summary>How often should I come in for a cleaning and exam?</summary><p>Most patients benefit from visits every six months. If you have a history of gum disease or other concerns, we may recommend more frequent checkups.</p></details>
            <details><summary>What if I haven't been to the dentist in years?</summary><p>That's more common than you'd think—and you're always welcome here without judgment. We'll start with a thorough exam and take things one step at a time.</p></details>
            <details><summary>Are digital X-rays safe?</summary><p>Yes. Digital X-rays emit significantly less radiation than traditional film X-rays and give us much clearer images to work with.</p></details>
            <details><summary>Do you see children as well as adults?</summary><p>Absolutely. We provide gentle, age-appropriate care for patients of all ages, from toddlers to seniors.</p></details>
            <details><summary>What should I expect at my first appointment?</summary><p>A conversation about your health history, followed by a full exam and cleaning. We'll walk you through everything we find before recommending any treatment.</p></details>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <aside>
        <div class="scard reveal">
          <div class="hd"><div class="grid-ov"></div><h3>Book a cleaning or checkup</h3><p>Most appointments 45–60 min</p></div>
          <div class="bd">
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 2"/></svg><span>Flexible morning and afternoon slots</span></div>
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg><span>Most insurance accepted &amp; verified up front</span></div>
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2 4 5v6c0 5 3.5 9 8 11 4.5-2 8-6 8-11V5l-8-3z"/></svg><span>ADA, CDC &amp; OSHA safety protocols</span></div>
            <div class="divider"></div>
            <a class="btn" href="/contact">Book a Cleaning or Checkup</a>
            <a class="btn btn-out" href="tel:7148932106" style="justify-content:center">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<ServiceExplore />

</Layout>
